- Most prolific Goodreads shill account creator.
- Most prolific Goodreads fake review creator.
- Most prolific Goodreads list spammer.

That&#39;s just this book!!! Add together all the shilling and spamming you do for you other books and nobody&#39;s ever gonna come close... ;)</a>
